        "subject": "=🎨 Image request: {{ $('7 · Prepare Designer Package').first().json.topic }}",
        "message": "=<h2>New image request for a LinkedIn post</h2>\n<p><strong>Topic:</strong> {{ $('7 · Prepare Designer Package').first().json.topic }}</p>\n<h3>Post draft</h3>\n<p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">{{ JSON.parse($('7 · Prepare Designer Package').first().json.draft_content).post_text }}</p>\n<h3>Image guidelines</h3>\n<p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">{{ $('7 · Prepare Designer Package').first().json.image_brief }}</p>\n<h3>How to deliver</h3>\n<p>Host the final image anywhere that gives a public direct link (Slack file, Google Drive, Dropbox…), then paste the link into this form:</p>\n<p><a href=\"{{ $execution.resumeFormUrl }}\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:10px 18px;background:#0a66c2;color:#fff;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none\">Submit image →</a></p>\n<p>The workflow continues automatically once you submit.</p>",
